{"tid":1696021,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"全民屎尿師上線了","createTime":"2019-11-06T02:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T05:19:45.000Z","uid":8850,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"49602e415bc8a280170808e5338791934d614585","tid":1696021,"uid":8850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"[美食] 唔敢食屎但敢玩雞蛋嘅入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1683882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1683882</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n首先對屎魔法師致敬<br />\n小弟真係接受唔到存放屎係屋企<br />\n但尿呢？<br />\n我接受到<br />\n畢竟無咁大味 又乾淨企理<br />\n<br />\n大家都知啲tg分分鐘污染咗水喉架啦<br />\n所以大家買多啲枝裝水番屋企飲<br />\n飲完又可以屙番落去<br />\n又唔洗沖廁 <br />\n一來慳水費 <br />\n二來環保 <br />\n三來又可以保障自己身體健康<br />\n儲滿晒之後點做 大家自由發揮啦<br />\n<br />\n唉吔  突然醒起屋企有啲雞蛋臭咗㖭<br />\n我咋咋淋處理咗佢先<br />\n唔講住 係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOnorjr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLOnorjr.png&h=0e598b1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a93d898ab7a705079662e923a796db7c356afa1","tid":1696021,"uid":76133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"係黨鐡上線唔知會點.<br />\n<br />\n個站又臭, 車箱又臭. 仲邊有人搭."},{"pid":"7328d41122bdf86ee7962ed2736f313a8e8f8198","tid":1696021,"uid":8850,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0a93d898ab7a705079662e923a796db7c356afa1","tid":1696021,"uid":76133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"係黨鐡上線唔知會點.<br />\n<br />\n個站又臭, 車箱又臭. 仲邊有人搭."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不嬲黨鐵都有蝗周圍屙"},{"pid":"02e7a08ac5199ac470210043634ba63be09f3031","tid":1696021,"uid":122134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"樓主近排都幾熱氣"},{"pid":"dfd2a5904e73e2cb20df754ad7376d3365b07460","tid":1696021,"uid":8850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"